Title: A Knapsack Problem
Description: If there is one thing I have learned in my years as a seamstress, $p, it is that you can never have enough space for your reagents. In fact, we could use a few more bags around here to hold everything. Would you mind stitching another?
ObjectivesText: Craft 1 Simply Stitched Reagent Bag for Fulafong in Valdrakken.
